{"/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_weimaraner_ver02/data/sn83045462/00280656203/1907121901/0189.xml":{"full_text":"Store\nNew York?WASHINGTON?Paris.\nRemain Open Evenings Until 9 G'Clock.\nThis Is Everybody's Christmas Store.\nO matter where one turns tlhere is brightness and beauty and holiday thought. And, with its brightness and beauty, it\nis also the safest sort off a store for Christmas shopping. Command off the markets lets us name the fairest prices, even\nfor the kind of things that you think will be dear. Every department is overflowing with gift things for Christmas, care=\nfully selected in the world's best markets, and they are marked at uniformly moderate prices.\nThe store works more smoothly in a Christmas crowd than ever before, and yet the crowd gets bigger and bigger every day,\nBetween now and Christmas we shall seE3 and deliver more things=twice more=than any other time in the year. This\nmeans that we shall have twice as many chances to make mistakes, and twice as much opportunity to serve you well.\nThe mistakes we have guarded against by the most careful examination and increase of our facilities, and by exhorting our\npeople to be more than ever careful in getting your right name and address and other directions. Will you help us, as far as\npossible, by seeing that they do it while you are there to set them right?\nAnd please carry small parcels with you when practicable.\nSilks for Xmas Presents. !!!!\"!?'Saie of\nILKS are always an appropriate, useful and acceptable Christ\nmas present, whether in dress, skirt or waist lengths. To\nselect from we offer a very large and varied stock:\n\nPeau de Cygne, Armure, Brocade,\nMessaline, Satin Majestic, Peau de Soie,\nSatin Duchesse, Taffetas, Electra,\nMoire Antique, Chevron, Victoria,\nMoire Velour, Ottoman, Habutai,\nLiberty Satin, Faille Francaise, Plaids,\nSurah, Gros Grain, Crepe de Chine, etc.\nWe will cut any desired length for a dress, skirt or waist and\nput it up in a neat box. The box protects and adds grace to the\ngift.\nWe are showing in our Silk Department\n24-Inch Crepe de Chine,\nIn a great variety of beautiful and unique designs and many color\nings. These goods were especially designed for Head Throws and\nTheater and Automobile Scarfs. 2% yards required for a scarf.\nSpecial price, 11.00 per yard.\nWe show also as appropriate Christmas gifts:\nHand-Embroidered Japanese Silk Waists,\nIn white only, embroidered in self.\n$4.50 a waist pattern.\nHand- Embroidered Japanese Crepede Chi neWaists,\nVery elaborately embroidered, in white only, at\n$20.00 a waist pattern.\nSecond floor. G it.\nSilk Hosiery.\nGIFT that -woold meet\nwith the fullest apprecia\ntion.\nWc have just received\nand offer at a special price\nDozen Women's\nPure Silk Hose,\nin black, white, sky, pink, laven\nder, tan and cardinal. They arc\nsplendid quality, and a very spe\ncial value.\n$11,110 per pair.\n3 prs. for $3.00.\nRegular $1.50 quality.\nNeatly boxed for Christmas.\nMain floor. F st.\nHousehold Linens\nFor Xmas Gifts.\nAMASK Table Cloths and\nNapkiVis.\nHemstitched Damask\nDinner Sets.\nHand-embroidered Luncheon\nimJ-embroi$ered Linen Bed\nspi*?y*. I\nHaml-embroidered Centerpieces,\nD^ilieA. Bureau Scarfs. Afternoon\n)ths and Pillow Shams.\nHand-embroidered Linen Top\nSheets with Pillow Cases to\n^match,/-'\nHand-embroidered Crib Sheets,\nwith Pillow Slips to match.\nChiny Lace Doilies, Table\nCloths, Tea Cloths and Center\npieces.\nFine Madeira Hand-embroid\nered Doilies.\n6-inch. 25c each.\n<>-inch, 50c each.\n18-inch, $1.50 each.\n24-inch, $2.25 each.\nFine Madeira Hand-embroid\nered Bureau Scarfs.\n]8x3<>inch, $2.50 each.\ni8x45-inch, $3.00 each.\ni8x54-inch, $3.75 each.\nRenaissance Lace Bureau\nScarfs.\nl8x54-inch, $1.35 each.\nTorchon Lace Bureau Scarfs;\nsize i8x54-inch.\n$1.50. $1.75. $2.50 and $3.50 each.\nHand-drawn Japanese Linen\nBureau Scarfs,\nl8x54-inch, $1.00 each.\nHand-drawn Japanese Linen\nTable Covers.\ni8x54-inch, $1.25 each.\nSpecial:\nHandsome Open-work Linen\nTable Covers; size 63x63-inch.\n$5.00 each. Value, $10.00.\nDown Comfortables.\nEach quilt is filled with odorless\ndown and guaranteed not to shed.\nSatine-covered, $6.00 each.\nSilk-covered. $9.00 to $25.00 each.\nSecond floor, Eleventh st.\nWhite Dresses for\nInfants and Children.\nE are showing an ex\ncellent assortment of\ndainty Dresses, for\ninfants and children,\nmade of sheer nainsooks, fine cam\nbrics, India linons, madras, etc.. of\nforeign and domestic manufac\nture. Some are hand-made. All\nare neatly and becomingly\ntrimmed.\nOne or more of these pretty\ndresses would make a most serv\niceable gift for the baby.\nBoys' and Girls'\nSweaters for Gifts.\nPLENDID assortments,\nembracing all the good\nstyles in every desirable\ncolor and combination.\nJacket Sweaters, all wool. In white, red,\ngray and navy?attractive styles for boys\nand girls. Sires 5 to 14 years.\nEach ?PI-5?\nJacket Sweaters, fine and heavy, button\ndown-the-front style, in all the\npopular colors. Sixes 6 to 14 years.\nW\nGood. Heavy Sweaters, in navy, gray\nand garnet, with pretty color com\nblnatlons: size* 4 to 14 years. Each.*i-U\"\nToques or Stocking Caps, long and short\nstyles, in all the popular shades.\nEach, 25c, 50c and $1.00\nBoys' Bath Robes, In a great variety of\nmaterials and attractive colorings. Sizes\nR to 15 years. Special* o*\nprices, each $>3.00 $4.50\nBoys' Neckwcar, in all\nstyles, boxed for Xmas 25C ana 5?C\nThlrd floor, Tenth st.\nSofa Pillows.\n^C\\ OTHING adds to the fin\na1 I ish of a room more than\npillows. We have cush\nions of all kinds and de\nscriptions, for the sofa, the divan,\nthe den. the chair back.\nSpecials:\nA lot of Covered Pillows, in\nquaint Dutch and French sub\njects an exceptionally good\nvalue.\nSpecial price, $1.25 each.\nA lot of Covered Pillows, in un\nusually handsome embroidered ef\nfects, suitable for parlors, living\nrooms, dens, etc.\n$3.50 each. Value, $6.50.\nThese Covers, without the pil\nlow, $2.50 each.\nFourth floor, G st.\nSofa Cushions to Order.\nWe will make to your special\norder this week Sofa Cushions of\nany kind or style and deliver same\nat your specified time. Our large\nstock of rich silk damasks, bro\ncades, tapestries, etc., gives you a\nbroad choice for selection of hand\nsome covers.\nFourth floor, G st.\nArtistic Furniture\nPi!low Cords, Etc.\nThe things that give the pretty\nfinish tp the pillow. We show a\nlarge assortment of pillow cords\nand tassels, in plain and mixed\ncolors; also in gilt.\n35c to $1.00 each.\nFourth floor, G st.\nLace Bed Sets.\nfor Xmas Gifts.\nNainsook Short Presses, with tucks and inser\ntion to form yoke: ruffle on nee1- ?1\nsleeves; sizes 1 and 2 years. Each.\nNainsook Short Dresses, with tucks and feather\nstltchlng tr? form yoke; la re on neck and\nsleeves. Each /5<\nKainsook Short Dresses, with fine tucks and\nbox plaits to form yoke; ruffle on neck\nand sleeves. A style suitable for boys.\nEach $I.OO\nIndia I.inon Short Dresses, with tine tucks to\nform yoke; ruffle on neck and sleeves, c\nEach 5>I.OO\nIndia Linon Short Dresses, with tucks and lace\nInsertion to form yoke; lace on neck and sleeves\nskirt trimmed with lace-edged ruffle and C, ~r\ntucks. Each\nNainsook Short Dresses, with tucks and feath\nerstitching to form yoke; lace on neck c-. _\nand sleeves. Each 5>I.^O\nChildren's Hand-made Nainsook Short\nwith fine tucks to form yoke; lace on\nneck and sleeves. Each\nChildren's Hand-made Nainsook Short\nI with hand-embroidered yoke; lace on\nj neck and sleeves. Each\nI Children's Hand-made Nainsook Short,\nwith line tucks and featherstitchlng to\nform yoke; lace on neck and sleeves.\nEach\nThird floor. Eleventh st.\nDresses.\n$2.00\nDresses.\n$2-75\nDresses,\nS3.00\nCorsets and\nCorset Sets.\nE arc showing a most\ncarefully selected\nstock of Corsets, for\neign and domestic, in\nsatisfactory variety.\nPrices range up to $25.00.\nCorsets as Xmas gifts arc more\npopular than ever. They make\ndainty gifts, and are su